<TR><TD COLSPAN="2">
Programme written by: K.L. Ayres
</TD></TR>
<TR><TD COLSPAN="2">
K.L. Ayres &amp; D.J. Balding (1998). Measuring departures from Hardy-Weinberg:
a Markov chain Monte Carlo method for estimating the inbreeding
coefficient. <I>Heredity</I> <B>80</B>, 769-777
</TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN="CENTER">
